# the cure basil gimlet
# hannah & josh & emma

6 basil leaves
1.5 ounce gin
0.75 ounce lime
0.5 ounce simple

muddle basil w/ ice
build in shaker
shake


# pink pony cowboy
# josh and emma

build:

2 oz whiskey
1/2 oz raspberry simple syrup
2 dash cocoa bitter
1..2 oz prosecco

improvements?:
- use 2 oz bourbon
- add 3/4 oz lemon?
- use 3/4 oz syrup
- use 1 1/2 oz prosecco
- shake and top wine




# texlive install

https://www.tug.org/texlive/doc/install-tl.html
https://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/LaTeX/Installation
https://tug.org/texlive/doc/texlive-en/texlive-en.html#x1-50001.3
https://wiki.debian.org/TeXLive



curl -L -o install-tl-unx.tar.gz https://mirror.ctan.org/systems/texlive/tlnet/install-tl-unx.tar.gz
curl -L -o install-tl-unx.tar.gz https://mirror.ctan.org/systems/texlive/tlnet/install-tl-unx.tar.gz.sha512

# scheme-medium
# scheme-small
# scheme-basic
perl install-tl \
    -gui text \
    --paper=letter \
    --texdir $HOME/.texlive2024 \
    --scheme scheme-small \
    -no-interaction


use symlinks? or setup env:
see  3.4.1 Environment variables for Unix  https://tug.org/texlive/doc/texlive-en/texlive-en.html#x1-50001.3


tlmgr init-usertree
tlmgr install latex latex-bin latexconfig
tlmgr install biber biblatex
tlmgr install latex-fonts collection-fontsrecommended
tlmgr install pgf xcolor tikzfill tikzpagenodes tcolorbox pgfornament adforn
tlmgr install amsmath babel carlisle ec geometry graphics hyperref lm  marvosym oberdiek parskip graphics-def url
tlmgr update --self --all



